{"tid":1361852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花］ 勞工處職員給香港人的公開信","createTime":"2019-07-24T16:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T07:02:45.000Z","uid":20272,"like":200,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b3f1ec744e95ac12572a44571678b4046d079f","tid":1361852,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:48:41.000Z","msg":"一封勞工處職員給香港人的公開信<br />\n<br />\n致各位香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群熱愛香港的勞工處職員，年資有深有淺，來自不同範疇的工作崗位。我們雖然不是紀律部隊，沒有能力站在前線直接守護市民，但作為人民公僕，我們一直盡心盡力，默默服務香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n對於近月因逃犯條例修訂議案引起的社會紛爭，我們表示極度痛心及遺憾。同為人民公僕的警察淪為國家統治機器，連番使用過量武力作出清場甚或驅散並圍堵示威者，而當中不乏仍在就學的年青人，實在令人痛心；而作為特區政府首長，林鄭月娥漠視民意，面對數以百萬計反對聲音依然故我，甚或稱自己為香港母親，實屬遺憾。容我們講句：恥與為伍。<br />\n<br />\n由六月九日，一百萬人大遊行，換來特首輕輕一句二讀工作會如期進行；<br />\n<br />\n六月十二日，金鐘發生警民衝突，警方使用布袋彈及橡膠子彈等較高武力，行動中子彈擊中示威者頭部，警務處處長即日定義為暴動；<br />\n<br />\n六月十五日，特首宣布因為發生六月十二日的衝突，修例工作會暫緩執行，同日晚上發生第一宗殉道；<br />\n<br />\n六月十六日，二百萬零一人的香港有史以來最大型遊行，林鄭政府依然對市民的五大訴求不聞不問；<br />\n<br />\n七月一日，示威者衝擊立法會，林鄭凌晨四點開記者會譴責示威者衝擊香港法治；<br />\n<br />\n七月六日，光復屯門示威，警方因保護施襲者而在沒有警告下使用胡椒噴劑；<br />\n<br />\n七月七日，九龍區大遊行，晚上旺角衝突有警員挑釁市民「隻揪」；<br />\n<br />\n七月十三日，光復上水遊行及示威，警方在追捕示威者時，導致一名年僅十八歲的示威者被追至跳橋；<br />\n<br />\n七月十四日，沙田區大遊行，晚上警方直闖城市廣場進行無理的清場行動，嚇倒不少無辜市民；<br />\n<br />\n直到七月二十一日，上環圍堵中聯辦，警方在沒有舉旗警告下發射至少36發橡膠子彈並再次擊中示威者頭部；<br />\n<br />\n同日晚上，元朗發生白衣人大規模攻擊市民的事件，警方不但沒有即時執法，甚至砌詞狡辯，聲稱沒有目擊白衣人攜帶武器。<br />\n<br />\n人在做，天上看。最近兩星期在沙田、上環及元朗發生的事件更突顯香港警察在執法上的偏頗。對此，我們予以最嚴厲的譴責。本處亦有執法部門，明白依例執法的重要。惟我們亦明白法例賦予我們權力，並不代表我們能夠過度行使。有法不依，有例不循只會官逼民反。<br />\n<br />\n我們懇請各位警察同事毋忘服務市民的初衷，虛心瞭解市民的想法，在各自崗位盡忠職守，保障市民生命財產理應是最重要的任務。不可再因為政治原因罔顧市民的安危，應盡快將元朗襲擊事件的涉事者及策劃者繩之於法，避免同類型事件再次發生，以免市民人心惶惶。<br />\n<br />\n我們亦懇請各位繼續以和平理性的方式表達訴求，並聆聽及接納更多不同的意見。多元社會是香港賴以生存的基石，和而不同亦是香港價值重要一環。<br />\n<br />\n解鈴還需繫鈴人，我們在此促請政府高層以冷靜、真誠、謙卑的心去聆聽社會各界意見，努力修補社會撕裂。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我們要為遲來的發聲向各位道歉。很抱歉，作為公務員我們的宗旨是不偏不倚，因此在政治事件上我們沒有太多發表意見的空間。不過當社會出現不公義時，保持中立等於站在壓逼者的一方。我們時刻銘記香港人這個身份，勇於站在市民一方。<br />\n<br />\n未來，我們會繼續貫切 &quot;以民為本&quot; 的精神，在各自崗位克盡己任。希望各位能支持我們的工作。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n一群熱愛香港的勞工處職員上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hH3jTbZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhH3jTbZ.png&h=a7692549&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vUkaZRZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvUkaZRZ.png&h=d0c5d1d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FEtctLk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFEtctLk.png&h=95050197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCPryb1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCPryb1.png&h=401a10ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g506yb1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg506yb1.png&h=3e3d24db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GPWBaYH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGPWBaYH.png&h=d9b68410&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5yjTb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5yjTb2.png&h=376e3bdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEJWVqo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEJWVqo.png&h=d6eb8343&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a34e684a89d4bb90a8781774b664a9ed34a81e55","tid":1361852,"uid":196006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ibb.co/dJBhYck\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fibb.co%2FdJBhYck&h=013b5353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ibb.co/mNCFh6x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fibb.co%2FmNCFh6x&h=8e930708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n代老友支持"},{"pid":"5883b366f341cc55efb517ec33a377cae4427f5a","tid":1361852,"uid":20272,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"如閣下亦為熱愛香港的勞工處職員，但不便直接上載僱員身分證，可考慮send 去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">tg：@LabourD</span></span>。收到後我們會post 在此。感謝各位。"},{"pid":"a05bf995b8eff68d9a48d48ab20a83ddeb3549df","tid":1361852,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a34e684a89d4bb90a8781774b664a9ed34a81e55","tid":1361852,"uid":196006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ibb.co/dJBhYck\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fibb.co%2FdJBhYck&h=013b5353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ibb.co/mNCFh6x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fibb.co%2FmNCFh6x&h=8e930708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n代老友支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:52:30.000Z","msg":"感謝支持，但係巴打死link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78db0104144106a8c4834a05cec64802dc246e73","tid":1361852,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:57:55.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f603699680f5c0dd82f8eeb695272c7521686b5","tid":1361852,"uid":198595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1ecfdbb8244cc193e0e7c134cb21fb669c65d056","tid":1361852,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:00:15.000Z","msg":"不如一齊罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259ea0cd5d0573751e3630d702c478efd1bd4b10","tid":1361852,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:01:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5b8f575ce540f1d0943c5bf5bc13d4b0ca8bd82","tid":1361852,"uid":42970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9fe9390f2082564274ff6b73502af55d15296af","tid":1361852,"uid":92500,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:01:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb2040d5425c4dccb472ae699c1c7db5c135f0e1","tid":1361852,"uid":17547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:01:53.000Z","msg":"勞記好波！"},{"pid":"5c73160104cb64f70f92de11b122cba4100315a5","tid":1361852,"uid":237077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>更正版文宣</strong></span></span><br />\n盡貼大家共識 呢張最主要係想叫到多啲人參加<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67aycf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67aycf2.jpg&h=98790fe1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e95478bd904911ad2438f178951786ad9a10b29e","tid":1361852,"uid":37135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83843b3661bcc11f4f40091a24212156dfe0c5b5","tid":1361852,"uid":267189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:39:20.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲<br />\n小弟見到好多遍地開花嘅post，好感動<br />\n不同行業嘅巴絲都出嚟發聲<br />\n<br />\n但係因為連登啲post好散同埋facebook接觸到嘅年齡層面相對連登會更加廣<br />\n所以開一個facebook page去整合一啲政府部門同公營機構嘅遍地開花post裡面嘅相<br />\n<br />\n點解淨係整政府部門同公營機構呢？<br />\n因為佢哋發聲嘅震撼力比較大同埋小弟能力有限，未能夠整合晒各行各業嘅post<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲其實只係想post喺連登，而唔想擺喺facebook，歡迎pm我，我會即刻delete返<br />\n<br />\n而如果有喺政府部門或者公營機構工作嘅巴絲想post去facebook，歡迎喺facebook pm呢個page: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivilservantsflowers&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0KtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=5380819b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"bd7d92bb12fd426f62843cd2481aa7ee9ba064a